00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:22,220
But your appearance

312
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:24,420
calmed me down instantly.

313
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:27,110
I wasn't thinking about

314
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,420
