341
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:35,980
Congratulations.

342
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,070
Your love is more solid than gold.

343
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:41,740
Thank you.

344
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:00,180
Please come in.

