353
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:14,740
That's good.

354
00:23:17,390 --> 00:23:18,790
How are you doing lately?

355
00:23:20,660 --> 00:23:21,830
I'm fine.

356
00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:23,390
You don't have to worry about me.

