379
00:24:18,220 --> 00:24:18,790
Hello.

380
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:19,500
Ms. Xing.

381
00:24:19,870 --> 00:24:21,110
How are you feeling?

382
00:24:21,180 --> 00:24:22,310
When will you be discharged?

383
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:23,140
Tomorrow.

384
00:24:23,420 --> 00:24:24,350
That's great.

385
00:24:24,630 --> 00:24:26,590
The Love Special of
Evergreen Clinic's Dr. Wang

