406
00:25:32,660 --> 00:25:34,590
Think, where have you seen me before?

407
00:25:39,870 --> 00:25:41,030
You are Shenzhi.

408
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:42,700
Yes.

409
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:46,550
You wanted a wedding ceremony
