475
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,420
That's why I had to call Mr. Lu.

476
00:30:04,630 --> 00:30:06,350
Your dad's clock is ticking.

477
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:09,110
Don't you want to go in and have a look?

478
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:36,740
Shen.

479
00:30:38,460 --> 00:30:39,220
Shen.

480
00:30:42,460 --> 00:30:43,740
Xingruo is here to see you.

481
00:30:57,550 --> 00:30:58,220
Don't get excited.

482
00:31:02,700 --> 00:31:03,500
