00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:51,790
But you coming to see me today

525
00:34:51,790 --> 00:34:54,230
and talking it out,

526
00:34:57,060 --> 00:34:58,790
I am contented.

527
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:03,580
I hope your life will be

528
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:05,230
