552
00:38:10,620 --> 00:38:11,420
And to meet you.

553
00:38:14,870 --> 00:38:16,390
Okay, that's enough talking.

554
00:38:17,540 --> 00:38:18,710
From now on,

555
00:38:19,350 --> 00:38:21,190
