556
00:38:23,390 --> 00:38:23,940
Goodbye.

557
00:38:51,270 --> 00:38:52,870
I have always thought

558
00:38:54,310 --> 00:38:55,540
of myself as a child.

559
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:00,270
But now,

